<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I have a query with having clause.
The binds data are empty here:</p>

<p>line #217</p>

<pre class="literal">
$rowCount = $db-&gt;select()-&gt;from($this-&gt;_select);
</pre>

<p>my workaround:</p>

<pre class="literal">
$rowCount = $db-&gt;select()-&gt;bind($this-&gt;_select-&gt;getBind())-&gt;from($this-&gt;_select);
</pre>

